Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Ndon't care what people think about them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Nfollow what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down a difficult road\Nfilled with endless struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you are going\Nfollowing someone else's map?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An insightful crow comes along\Nto tear up the map
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now open your eyes and\Ntake a look at the truth (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to lose,\Nso let's GO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Ndon't care what people think about them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Dreamers\Nfollow what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oli Oli Oli Oh!\NJust go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)\NWe're gonna do it and do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Bang)\NHit it straight like a line drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here right now (Burn)\NWe're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Good-bye, Sensei.\N– Yay! School's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye, Iruka Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you practice what\NI taught you today, Transform Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And tell your family about tomorrow’s\Ninauguration for the Fifth Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Okay! 					– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konohamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Iruka Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…it’s all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay… Goodbye, Iruka Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he got over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your way back from rehabilitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um…yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To activate each and\Nevery cell all at once…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were just one by one,\Nit’d be a snap,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but all of them together\Nis gonna be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leaf Village is\Nin great trouble right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we must do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think if you had Lady Tsunade take\Na look, you'd get better very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better that you give up being\Na Shinobi and look for a different path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei and Student:\NThe Bond of the Shinobi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, young kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The medal of youth is one of passion,\Nwith no looking back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you work hard at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m telling you, son,\Nyou will become a fine Shinobi! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?\NHe is pretty overbearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son, be ambitious! Bloom of Youth…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, adieu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time I met Guy Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you have all become Genin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear what\Nyour goals are for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to prove that\NI could become a splendid Ninja,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I can’t use\NNinjutsu or Genjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the ultimate for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are good serious eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become a respectable Ninja\Neven only with Taijutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you realize that\Nif you can’t use Ninjutsu or Genjutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you’re not a Ninja in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you remember being told\Nthat you’re the first person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to graduate from the academy\Nwho’s only able to use Taijutsu ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not because you’re so good;\Nit’s just that you’re unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:05:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! If you have passion,\Nit’s not necessarily so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you act with passion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,compete with good rivals\Nand lift each other up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can all become great Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,\Nyou have to work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passion…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…was inspired by Guy Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By his words…and his deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re late!\N17 minutes and 32 seconds late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s not do it today, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of us has 48 wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a win today,\None of us will pull ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you won't give up\Neven if I say I wouldn’t want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my turn to choose the event, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! What’s it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Taijutsu battle? A 100-meter dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding our breath under water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care, we could even\Nhave an eating contest…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors?\NThat’s what you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that your luck is\None part of your skill, don’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it’s a great competition\Nfor testing your observational reflexes…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get the feeling\NKakashi’s just playing around with Guy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‘cuz he can't be bothered?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what it looks like to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept the battle.\NThere’s no way I’m gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, I’ll walk around the Leaf Village\N500 times on my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one of your special,\Nself-imposed rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can’t do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s ridiculous.\NHe’s acting like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that’s impossible,\Neven for Guy Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible? Reckless, I’d say!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Rock, paper…!\N– Rock, paper…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guy Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you skipped out\Non rehabilitation these past two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t be doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first became Genin…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is where I revealed\Nmy dream, my aspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neji laughed at me then,\Nbut I meant what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to prove that\NI could become a splendid Ninja
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I can't use\NNinjutsu or Genjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the ultimate for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, you told me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you act with passion,\Ncompete with rivals,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can become a fine Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do that, it’d take “effort.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Transform! 					– Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because while at the academy…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one, not one friend or teacher,\Nsaid that kind of thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put me at ease…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You opened up a path\Njust when I was unsure of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized all I had to do\Nwas try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I complained that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all my efforts couldn’t match\Nthe others’ natural talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you told me that I had\Na natural talent for effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I learned the importance\Nof believing in my own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance of a successful surgery\Nis probably 50%, at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:11:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…this is one time…\Neven if I try my best…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even if I believe in myself,\Nthere’s nothing in the world I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guy Sensei… Please tell me…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me.\NCan I become like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this kind of thing\Nhappen only to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have my own\NWay of Ninja to follow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my own dreams and aspirations\Nthat I have to protect and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,prove to the world even\Nif it means dying for…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight Inner Gates…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Forbidden Jutsu that\Nwill destroy the body of the practitioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m prepared for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me that Forbidden Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is…for my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to become a great Ninja\Nrelying only on Taijutsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, that’s all you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be so painful for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it seems that your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all your wishes\Nare being cruelly taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not matter what his wishes are,\Nhe should give up on becoming a Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be free of that pain,\Nyou have to prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean…\Nto prepare to give up my dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose your dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will undergo pain even greater\Nthan what you feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither you nor I would be able to\Ngo on living if we lose the Way of Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What fools we are…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee! Have the surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How’s it going with Cell Activation Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all about the Chakra, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many kinds of cells…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,skin cells, internal organ cells,\Nmuscular cells…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it’s just a tad difficult\Nto activate all of them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?\N“Just a tad,” you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you testing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m declaring my trust in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why,\Nbut just a while ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was remembering the time\Nwhen you and Kakashi Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were competing\Nwith rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, Kakashi Sensei said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your luck is\None part of your skill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This surgery is also fifty-fifty,\Nlive or die…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s not a game of\Nrock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what happened\Nafter that, Lee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500 times around…\Nlt’s a promise! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose, I’ll walk 500 times\Naround the Leaf Village, on my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can’t do that! That’s stupid.\NHe’s acting like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing here, Lee?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi Sensei is not here.\Nln fact, no one is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a man stands cool with\Na Nice-guy pose in front of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he should keep his promise,\Neven if it kills him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you’re about to start\Ndoing something,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why do you always come up\Nwith some kind of crazy rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question, Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really know how\Nto get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I’ll tell you.\NBut remember, you can’t tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making self-rules is nothing less than\Na practice which brings me victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Self-rules…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The point of these rules is that,\Nwhen you’re going after something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they push you into a real tough spot…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about chaining yourself down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, on the other side\Nof the hellish rule that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“If I lose at rock, scissors, paper,\NI’ll do 500 laps” is the idea that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“If I do 500 laps,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s no way I won’t be able\Nto beat Kakashi next time.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They hold power,\Nthe potential of the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By being chained down\Nto doing 500 laps,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it makes you get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even about things like\Nrock, paper, scissors competitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which are so trifling otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, even if you lose,\Nwalking around the village 500 times
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,give you the benefit\Nof extremely intense training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I’ve gotta do a little more.\NHere we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going with you!\NI have my own “self-rule” which is--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Don’t push yourself, Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can’t keep up with you, I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,try even harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, I’ll aim to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I keep trying,\NI’ll be able to become a great Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! If that’s the case,\Nthen I have an addition to my rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can’t keep up with me\Nall the way to the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll put every ounce of\Nmy being into training you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I train you with all my being,\Nyou’ll be able to turn into a fine Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time you told me about\Nthe "self-rule," wasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your surgery will be a success
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you have worked hard\Nall the way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the power to bring\Nyour own future in the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the one in a thousand…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, one in a million chance\Nthat something goes wrong…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will die with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my Way of Ninja has been to\Nnurture you into a fine Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither you nor I would be able\Nto go on living if we lose the Way of Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What fools we are…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Guy Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, let’s go, Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tsunade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this day forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the ruler of the Village Hidden\Nin the Leaves, the Fifth Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your promise,\Nits a true heart give me courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always I feel it\Nthe precious time with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your still shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the wind that blows\Ntowards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city lights are like pieces of stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hold us together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Each one of us glows differently,”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you say laughingly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you look most dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a comet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the rainbow after the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bring light into my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being lost can be the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s promise we won’t cheat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... like a shooting star,\Nwe do go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! He has no hole\Nin his defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being impatient won't\Ndo any good, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's utilize the next mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:22:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The next mission\Nrequires an overnight stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Our chance will be at the inn.\N– Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get to the inn,\Nwe'll wait until he's defenseless…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– and then… 					– and then…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– unmask him at once!\N– unmask him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Gotta See! Gotta Know!\NKakashi Sensei's True Face!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz we're really curious!
